Source attribution / 出典について:

Each dataset carries its own primary sources in `meta.sources[]` and
`slices[].sources[]`. Most Japanese government sources are provided under the
Public Data License 1.0 (PDL-1.0), which requires attribution and a statement
that the material has been edited/adapted, and prohibits presenting the data
as if it were an official government work. See NOTICE.md for the required
attribution format and the full source list.

本データは各 dataset の meta.sources に記載した一次資料を基に編集・加工して
作成したものであり、出典元機関が作成・公表したものではありません。
再配布・引用時は NOTICE.md の出典表記に従ってください。
